# 🧠 BrainBoost AI
> Private chatbot · Runs entirely in your browser · Zero cost · by **Vrishab Varun**

## What's new
- 💬 Full chat UI with iMessage-style bubbles
- 🧠 Conversation memory (remembers last 6 turns)
- 🚀 Smarter models — LaMini-T5 (fast) + TinyLlama Chat (smart)
- ✨ Quick-start chips on the welcome screen
- 🗑 Clear conversation button

## Models
| Mode | Model | Size | Notes |
|------|-------|------|-------|
| ⚡ Fast | `Xenova/LaMini-Flan-T5-783M` | ~400 MB | Instruction-tuned, greedy decoding |
| 🧠 Smart | `Xenova/TinyLlama-1.1B-Chat-v1.0` | ~600 MB | Chat-tuned, sampling |

## Deploy to GitHub Pages
```bash
git init && git add . && git commit -m "BrainBoost AI"
git remote add origin https://github.com/YOU/brainboost-ai.git
git push -u origin main
# GitHub → Settings → Pages → Branch: main / root
```

## Run locally
```bash
python3 -m http.server 8080
# open http://localhost:8080
```

